            "chunk_index": 1,
            "text": "Daily Tribune, August 12, 2022; 118 OG No. 33, 9212 (August 15, 2022)\n\n[ REPUBLIC ACT NO. 11896, July 01, 2022 ]\n\nAN ACT DIVIDING BARANGAY MUZON IN THE CITY OF SAN JOSE DEL MONTE, PROVINCE OF BULACAN INTO FOUR (4) SEPARATE AND INDEPENDENT BARANGAYS TO BE KNOWN AS BARANGAY MUZON PROPER, BARANGAY MUZON EAST, BARANGAY MUZON WEST AND BARANGAY MUZON SOUTH\n\nBe it enacted by the Senate and House of Representatives of the Philippines in Congress assembled:\n\nSECTION 1.\n\nDivision of Barangay Muzon\n\n. â Barangay Muzon in the City of San Jose del Monte, Province of Bulacan is hereby divided into four (4) separate and independent barangays to be known as Barangay Muzon Proper, Barangay Muzon East, Barangay Muzon West and Barangay Muzon South.",
            "metadata": {
                "law_id": "RA_11896",
                "date": "July 01, 2022"
            }
        },
        {
